{
  "stem": "3453.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a danger, not just to us, but for the people of the small town, of the small village, of this small village.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Shimon Paikow decided that he must be eliminated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got rid of him so he could walk no more and could not do any harm to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From that point, I wanted to join a big group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was not-- I wanted to fight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I heard-- we heard Partisans are getting organized.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You asked me who were the Partisans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who were there?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What kind of-- who are the people?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were escapees from the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some people who couldn't stomach the Nazis, who were against the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They organized.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the-- the escapees, the-- the POWs escaped from hell and they were murdering just like the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were murdering them just like they were murdering the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In his camp, he tells you exactly what he's going to do, but people didn't pay attention.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He did it, all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there-- I heard it's a big group are coming through the woods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In a [NON-ENGLISH], we call it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH]-- a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's immovable They were [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were [NON-ENGLISH]-- I have-- in Russian, I am telling you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], it means local.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were sitting down there in the woods in one place and then go out on assignments, just rob the trains and do hell, whatever they could.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were, this group, what I'm talking, what I joined it was a moveable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I walked up with my friend down there, I saw the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I saw, you know, the people on-- the Partisans on horses with guns, machine guns, with grenades.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Even we had anti-tank.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH], we called it, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
